summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4568 for the improvement of Keen Way, from Woodland Park Avenue to North 67th Street and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues, by paving, and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 53330, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
